AngloGold to Almost Double Brazil Gold Output, Valor Reports

-- B y   L u c i a   K a s s a i
-- 
2011-07-11T12:10:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-11/anglogold-to-almost-double-brazil-gold-output-valor-reports.html
AngloGold Ashanti Ltd. (AU)  plans to
almost double gold output in  Brazil  by 2020, Valor Economico
reported, citing the head of the Brazilian unit, Helcio Guerra.  AngloGold plans to boost output to 880,000 troy ounces,
from 449,000 this year, he told the Sao Paulo-based newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lucia Kassai in Sao Paulo at 
 lkassai@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dale Crofts at   dcrofts@bloomberg.net . 